Package com.safenetinc.luna.provider.signature Description

JCA-compliant implementation of message signing and verification mechanisms using keys on the Luna HSM for LunaProvider. Only accessed from Luna provider framework. You should just refer to these classes for an idea of the provided mechanisms.
